OL,3,CThe game with no rules: What is Uppies
OL,4,Cand Downies?
OL,6,FOur reporter Kieran Macfadzean went
OL,7,Falong to find out why the game is so
OL,8,Fimportant.
OL,10,FA west Cumbrian town is preparing for
OL,11,Fthe return of a centuries-old mass
OL,12,Fgame with no rules.
OL,14,FUppies and Downies is a tradition
OL,15,Fwhich kicks off in Workington every
OL,16,FGood Friday.
OL,18,FFiercely contested, the winning team
OL,19,Fwill have bragging rights for the
OL,20,Fcoming year.
