OL,4,Cand Downies?
OL,6,FWhat are the rules of Uppies and
OL,7,FDownies?
OL,9,FThere is a gentleman's agreement
OL,10,Fbetween both sides that players are
OL,11,Fnot permitted to take the ball into a
OL,12,Fvehicle during a game.
OL,14,FBut - there are no official rules.
OL,16,FDownie Pat Carr said: "I started on my
OL,17,Fdad's shoulders to keep me safe. When
OL,18,FI was 11 it was the first time I
OL,19,Ftouched the ball. I got the buzz for
OL,20,Fit ever since. I've hailed three
OL,21,Fballs."
