OL,6,FHe added: "It's one of the best
OL,7,Fadrenaline rushes you'll ever get."
OL,9,FThree games are played each year, with
OL,10,Fthe first on Good Friday, the second
OL,11,Fon the Tuesday after Easter and the
OL,12,Ffinal one on the following Saturday.
OL,14,FBeyond Easter, the game is
OL,15,Fcommemorated all year round with a
OL,16,Fpair of coal-black iron-ore coloured
OL,17,Ffigure statues created by Maryport
OL,18,Fsculptor Colin Telfer. One is outside
OL,19,FWorkington Hall, and the other is at
OL,20,Fthe town harbour.
