OL,3,CThe game with no rules: What is Uppies
OL,4,Cand Downies?
OL,6,FEach year, participants raise money
OL,7,Ffor good causes. This year's charity
OL,8,Fis Andy's Man Club, a men's suicide
OL,9,Fprevention charity.
OL,11,FUppies and Downies is just one of
OL,12,Fabout 25 traditional football games
OL,13,Fstill played across Britain, with its
OL,14,Forigins tracing back to the 12th
OL,15,Fcentury.
OL,17,FThe modern tradition began sometime in
OL,18,Fthe latter half of the 19th century.
